 Home Loan Bank Boardapproving applications for insurance of accounts, including all conditionscontained therein, as in effect as August 9, 1989, are allocated to theOTS.<ITAG tagnum="21">Dated: at Washington, DC, this 3rd day of October 1989.</ITAG><ITAG tagnum="20">Office of Thrift supervision.</ITAG><ITAG tagnum="6">M. Danny Wall,</ITAG><ITAG tagnum="4">Director.</ITAG><ITAG tagnum="20">Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation.</ITAG><ITAG tagnum="6">L. William Seidman,</ITAG><ITAG tagnum="4">Chairperson.</ITAG><ITAG tagnum="40">[FR Doc. 89-23864 Filed 10-5-89; 8:45 am]</ITAG><ITAG tagnum="68">BILLING CODE 6720-01-M</ITAG></ITAG></ITAG></ITAG></TEXT></DOC>